arcade.patch.agent.action

Class PatchActionInsert

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.patch.agent.action.PatchActionInsert
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable

    public class PatchActionInsert
extends java.lang.Object
implements Action
    Implementation of Action for inserting cell agents.

    The action is stepped once after TIME_DELAY. The action will insert a mixture of INSERT_NUMBER cells from each of the registered populations into locations within the specified radius INSERT_RADIUS from the center of the simulation.

    See Also:
